{
  "stem": "11801.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 234.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And perhaps my mother was afraid that he would not recognize her, because she had changed a lot.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "At least in my mind she had changed a lot.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "She was-- when I saw her-- going back a little bit-- she didn't look anything like the woman that I remembered, perhaps, perhaps because she was so poorly dressed.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "I didn't mention that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And her arm had been broken in the camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "She had been shot.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "And so her arm was sort of deformed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "And it remained that way for the rest of her life.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "She refused to have it fixed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "She said, I can use my arm.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "My hands-- you know, she can do most things with her hand.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "She didn't want to take a chance on having somebody, you know, fiddle around with it and maybe make it worse than it was.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] perhaps she thought that nobody would recognize her.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so I, you know, with my red flag-- they couldn't help seeing me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So eventually I, I agreed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I put on my coat.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And here was this huge family that was meeting us at the boat-- aunts, uncles, cousins, what have you-- cousins on my mother's, on my mother's side-- her first cousins.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] my father was, to me, a total stranger.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had never been close to my father.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was a very quiet person, and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I would never have recognized him, although I'd seen a picture which he had sent to my mother.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Didn't look like the picture, either.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I think it was a very difficult reunion, as you can well imagine.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, what do you say-- what does a father say to a child he hasn't seen in eight years?",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
